## BinaryHeap.elements() method

Returns an iterator which retrieves elements in heap order.

This method does not change the existing binary heap.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
elements(): IterableIterator<T>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

IterableIterator&lt;T&gt;
